code: public boolean isEmpty() {     return (coordinate == null && (children == null || children.isEmpty())). }

protected int numDimensions() {     if (isEmpty()) {         throw new ElasticsearchException("attempting to get number of dimensions on an empty coordinate node").     }     if (coordinate != null) {         return Double.isNaN(coordinate.z) ? 2 : 3.     }     return children.get(0).numDimensions(). }

@Override public XContentBuilder toXContent(XContentBuilder builder, Params params) throws IOException {     if (children == null) {         builder.startArray().value(coordinate.x).value(coordinate.y).endArray().     } else {         builder.startArray().         for (CoordinateNode child : children) {             child.toXContent(builder, params).         }         builder.endArray().     }     return builder. }
